title: Crush a Grandmaster With The "Evil" Icelandic Gambit!
description:
#agadmator Challenge Cronaldinho to a game on Lichess https://lichess.org/@/cronaldinho

Pablo Zarnicki vs Fabian Fiorito
zt 2.5 (2000), Buenos Aires ARG, rd 4, Jul-29 
Scandinavian Defense: Icelandic-Palme Gambit (B01)

1. e4 d5 2. ed5 Nf6 3. c4 e6 4. de6 Be6 5. d4 Bb4 6. Bd2 Qe7 7. Bb4 Qb4 8. Qd2 Qe7 9. Qe3 Nc6 10. Nf3 Ng4 11. Qe2 O-O-O 12. h3 Rhe8 13. hg4 Qb4 14. Qd2 Bg4 15. Be2 Re2 16. Ke2 Nd4 17. Kf1 Qc4 18. Kg1 Nf3 19. gf3 Bf3 20. Rh3 Qg4 21. Rg3 Qh5 22. Rf3 Qf3
